Murray & Roberts Heads for Three-Month Low; to Report Loss for Full Year

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-08-19T11:46:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/murray-roberts-heads-for-three-month-low-to-report-loss-for-full-year.html
Murray & Roberts Holdings Ltd. (MUR) , a
South African construction company, headed for the weakest close
in three months after saying that its diluted loss will be as
much as 6.15 rand per share in the year through June.  The stock retreated 2.4 percent to 26.56 rand by 1:42 p.m.
in Johannesburg, heading for the lowest closing level since May
23.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  